data.description:
Well constructed 3 Bedroom brick ranch home with multiple baths, family room, sun room, 1 car attached garage, fire place, 2.15 +/- acres conveniently located in the Lewis Run Borough. There are many pluses to this property including a modern kitchen and hot water baseboard heating system. Sound inviting? It is! See for yourself!
The home sits on .32 of an acre (NOT located in a flood plain). The remaining 1.83 acreage is located in a flood plain.
